1) Problem Statement
Farmers face many challenges in agriculture today.
They often lack access to accurate weather information.
Many farmers do not know which crop is suitable for their soil and climate.
Poor planning of water, fertilizer, and labor increases farming costs.
Pest and disease detection usually happens too late, causing crop loss.
Also, farmers rarely get quick expert advice.
Because of these issues, productivity decreases and farmers face financial loss.

2) Proposed Solution
AgriConnect is a smart farming support platform that helps farmers manage crops and resources using technology.
The system provides:
Smart crop recommendations
Weather alerts and forecasts
Crop planning calendar
Resource management dashboard
Crop health monitoring
Farmer community and expert support
This platform helps farmers make data-driven decisions and improve productivity.

3) Key Features
1.Home
Overview of the platform
Latest farming tips and updates
2.Crop Recommendation
Suggests suitable crops based on soil type and season
3.Weather Updates
Real-time weather forecast
Rainfall and temperature alerts
4.Crop Calendar
Farming schedule (sowing, irrigation, fertilizing, harvesting)
5.Resource Management
Track water usage
Fertilizer usage
Farming expenses
6.Crop Health Detection
Upload crop images
Identify diseases or pests
7.Community / Farmer Forum
Farmers can ask questions
Share farming knowledge
8.Expert Advice
Agricultural expert suggestions and guidance
9.Profile
Farmer profile details
Farm information
10.Logout
